(136, 1, '2011-05-14 21:08:46', '2011-05-14 15:38:46', 'You can create your own module in minutes using the **Add custom tray icon feature**.\n\n\nTo create your own module, follow the steps listed below:\n\n* Set a title for your module.\n* Then upload a 16 x 16 PNG icon for your module.\n* Set a link that will open up on the click of the icon.\n* Select 1 from the 4 options available in the ‘Type’ dropdown box\n\nThere are four options:\n\n*1. Same Window* – Ideal for links part of your site (e.g. user registration page)	\n*2. New Window* – Recommended for links not part of your site (e.g. an advertisement)		\n*3. Popup* – Recommended for pages which are designed to open in a popup (e.g. chatrooms module is a popup). If you select this option, then you will have to set the *height* and *width* of the popup.		\n*4. Lightbox (same window popup)* - Module will open in a light box that floats overtop of the web page.\n\n![Modules - Custom Tray]\n(http://v6.cometchat.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/custom+tray-e1335960639118.png)', 'Add custom tray icon', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'add-custom-tray-icon', '', '', '2011-05-14 21:08:46', '2011-05-14 15:38:46', '', 4625, 'http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/?page_id=136', 11, 'page', '', 0),
(138, 1, '2011-05-14 21:13:56', '2011-05-14 15:43:56', '# Creating a Facebook Fan Page\n\nTo create a page, point your browser to [http://www.facebook.com/pages/create.php](http://www.facebook.com/pages/create.php)\n\n![Facebook - Create Fan Page](http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/media/6.png)\n\n&gt; CometChat does not allow use of Facebook Groups. You must create a Facebook Fan Page.\n\n# Configuring the module\n\nOn creation of a Facebook Fan Page, you will need to find your Facebook Fan Page ID.\n\nClick on the *Edit Page* link on your Facebook Fan Page and pay attention to the browser URL.\n\n![Facebook - Fan Page ID](http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/media/7.png)\n\nIn the above example, the Facebook Page ID is *106148049425133*\n\nOnce you have located your Page ID, go to *CometChat Administration Panel* -&gt; *Modules* -&gt; *Facebook Fan Page* -&gt; *config*\n\nEnter your Page ID in the *Facebook Fan Page ID* and empty the *Facebook Fan Page Name* box. Finally click on the *Update Settings* button.\n\n![CometChat - Facebook Fan Page](http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/media/8.png)\n', 'Facebook Fan Page', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'facebook-fan-page', '', '', '2011-05-14 21:13:56', '2011-05-14 15:43:56', '', 4625, 'http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/?page_id=138', 13, 'page', '', 0),
(140, 1, '2011-05-14 21:17:01', '2011-05-14 15:47:01', '# Creating a Twitter account\n\nTo create a Twitter account, point your browser to [http://www.twitter.com](http://www.twitter.com)\n\n![Twitter - Create New Account](http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/media/9.png)\n\n# Configuring the module\n\nOnce you have your Twitter username, go to *CometChat Administration Panel* -&gt; *Modules* -&gt; *Twitter* -&gt; *config*\n\nEnter your username in the *Twitter Username* and set *No of Followers* to *48* and *No of Tweet* to *12*. Finally click on *Update Settings* button.\n\n![CometChat - Twitter](http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/media/10.png)\n', 'Twitter', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'twitter', '', '', '2011-05-14 21:17:01', '2011-05-14 15:47:01', '', 4625, 'http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/?page_id=140', 31, 'page', '', 0),
(142, 1, '2011-05-14 22:05:06', '2011-05-14 16:35:06', '# Server Requirements\n\nCometChat is a web-based application and as such has a few minimum requirements. To run CometChat, you need a web hosting provider that includes the following things:\n\n1. PHP version 4 or greater\n2. MySQL version 4 or MSSQL Server 2005\n3. A pre-registered domain name\n4. 10 Megabytes of hard drive space\n5. PHP extensions: curl (required for some plugins)\n\nMost hosting providers already have these applications on their servers. With the above requirements meant, the CometChat software will run on any operating system using any modern web server software.\n\n# Browser Support\n\nWe support modern, standards-compliant web browsers, such as Internet Explorer 7+, Firefox 2+, Safari 3+, Chrome and Opera 9.5+\n\n## Audio/Video Chat and all other plugins\n\nSame requirements as that of CometChat Core. **No special hardware or software required.**\n\n## Screen Sharing Plugin\n\nIf you would like to use the screen sharing, you will need [RED5](http://www.red5.org) (open-source). The software can either be hosted on your own server or you can use a third-party host. [Contact us](/contact) for recommendations.\n\n## Whiteboard Plugin\n\nIf you would like to use whiteboard plugin, you will need either [RED5](http://www.red5.org) (open-source) or [Adobe FMS server](http://www.adobe.com/products/flash-media-server-family.html) (commercial). Both software can either be hosted on your own server or you can use a third-party host. [Contact us](/contact) for recommendations.\n\n## Real-time Translate Module\n\nIf you would like to use real-time translation (not to confuse with page translation), you must subscribe to either Microsoft or Google''s translation service. Microsoft provides a free subscription pack which maybe adequate for small/medium sites. Google charges $20 for 1 million characters and is not a monthly subscription. Learn more about [Microsoft''s pricing](http://go.microsoft.com/?linkid=9782667) and [Google''s pricing](http://code.google.com/apis/language/translate/v2/pricing.html).\n\n## Facebook/Gtalk Chat Extension\n\nAs this is a hosted solution, it is a free benefit we provide to all **active** CometChat license holders. If your license has expired, you can renew it for 50% of the edition price.', 'System Requirements', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'system-requirements', '', '', '2011-05-14 22:05:06', '2011-05-14 16:35:06', '', 165, 'http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/?page_id=142', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(146, 1, '2011-05-14 22:24:43', '2011-05-14 16:54:43', 'Installing CometChat with ready integration will only take you a few minutes. Please select a software from below. If your software does not feature below, please view the *Custom Coded Site* section.', 'Ready Integrations', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'ready-integrations', '', '', '2011-05-14 22:24:43', '2011-05-14 16:54:43', '', 4439, 'http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/?page_id=146', 2, 'page', '', 0),
