(499, 1, '2012-12-25 14:24:17', '2012-12-25 08:54:17', '<strong>Merry Christmas and a Happy New Year!</strong>\n\nAs the year approaches to an end, we celebrate and thank you! We''re incredibly grateful and humbled that you''ve selected CometChat to be an integral part of your site.\n\n<a href="http://www.cometchat.com/buy"><img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/happy2013.jpg" alt="" title="Happy Holidays!" width="600" height="600" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-503" /></a>\n\nCometChat has a come a long way in the last 4 years. We are constantly working on new features and have received a tremendous response for our latest version (v4.6). We have an interesting line-up of exciting enhancements in the coming year! So stay tuned and keep chatting...\n\nTo make this holiday season even more jolly, here is a 20% discount on any purchase (including upgrades!)\n\n<strong>Coupon Code: HAPPYHOLIDAYS\nValidity: Till 31st December</strong>\n\nSo what are you waiting for? <a href="http://www.cometchat.com/buy">Purchase</a> or <a href="http://www.cometchat.com/my">upgrade to a higher edition</a> of CometChat today!', 'Happy Holidays!', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'happy-holidays', '', '', '2012-12-25 14:24:17', '2012-12-25 08:54:17', '', 0, 'http://www.cometchat.com/blog/?p=499', 0, 'post', '', 0),
