(836, 1, '2012-06-01 16:01:44', '2012-06-01 10:31:44', 'To modify the incoming sound alert, follow the steps listed below:\n\n	<li><ol>\n\nCreate/find a new beep alert that you would like to use. The alert must be in MP3 format.</ol>\n</li>\n\n	<li><ol>\n\nReplace the <strong>cometchat/swf/beep.mp3</strong> with your new file.</ol>\n</li>\n\n<img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/alerts.png" alt="alerts" />\n\n	<li><ol>\n\nDelete the <strong>cometchat/swf/sound.swf file</strong>.</ol>\n\n</li>\n\n	<li><ol>\n\nRename <strong>cometchat/swf/sound_formp3.swf</strong> to <strong>cometchat/swf/sound.swf</strong></ol>\n\n</li>\n\n	<li><ol>\n\nClear your browser cache completely and hear your new beep play on incoming messages!</ol>\n\n</li>\n', 'How can I change the alert sound of my incoming messages?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'how-can-i-change-the-alert-sound-of-my-incoming-messages', '', '', '2012-06-01 16:01:44', '2012-06-01 10:31:44', '', 0, 'http://www.cometchat.com/answers/?p=836', 0, 'post', '', 0),
