(925, 1, '2012-06-01 16:29:29', '2012-06-01 10:59:29', 'Yes, our light-weight version is similar to Facebook''s chat look. To activate the light version, follow the steps listed below:\n\nLog into the <strong>Administration Panel</strong> and visit the <strong>Settings</strong> page.\n\nIn the setting page, set the <strong>Switch on light-weight chat?</strong> to <strong>Yes</strong>.\n\nAnd then click on the <strong>Update Settings</strong> button.\n\n<img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/lite+version.png" alt="Lite version" />\n\n<strong>Benefits</strong>\n\nBenefits of using light-weight feature:\n\n- Light weight removes certain functionality, thus reducing the load time as well\n- It gives you a feel of Facebook chat\n- Lite Version is unobtrusive and minimalistic\n\n\n<blockquote>Live Version does not allow the use of modules directly on the bar. However, they can be embedded in your site pages. Scroll bars will not be added if the width of chat-boxes (usually due to more than 4) is more than your browser width.</blockquote>\n', 'Is there a Facebook style theme for CometChat?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'is-there-a-facebook-style-theme-for-cometchat', '', '', '2012-06-01 16:29:29', '2012-06-01 10:59:29', '', 0, 'http://www.cometchat.com/answers/?p=925', 0, 'post', '', 0),
