(1040, 1, '2012-05-18 14:24:14', '2012-05-18 08:54:14', '# Configuring Report Conversation Plugin\n\nTo receive the incident reports from your users, enter your *Email Address* and click on the *Update Settings* button.\n\n![Report Conversation Setting]\n(http://v6.cometchat.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Report+Conversation+Setting1.png)\n', 'Report Conversation Plugin', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'report-conversation-plugin', '', '', '2012-05-18 14:24:14', '2012-05-18 08:54:14', '', 62, 'http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/?page_id=1040', 8, 'page', '', 0),
