(1224, 1, '2012-05-18 15:26:57', '2012-05-18 09:56:57', '# Configuring the module\n\nTo configure this module, set the values of the chatroom settings according to your requirements and then click on the *Update Settings* button.\n\n![Chatroom Modules]\n(http://v6.cometchat.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/chatroom+modules.png)', 'Chatrooms', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'chatrooms', '', '', '2012-05-18 15:26:57', '2012-05-18 09:56:57', '', 4625, 'http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/?page_id=1224', 16, 'page', '', 0),
