(1235, 1, '2012-08-23 14:23:44', '2012-08-23 08:53:44', 'The URL, for e.g <strong>http://yoursitename.com/chat/</strong> is meant to be accessed only through <strong>mobile devices</strong> and not by web browsers on the desktop/laptop machines. \n\nSo you can ignore this warning while checking this URL through web browsers on your desktop/laptop machines.\n', 'I get a warning "Sorry, your mobile browser does not support chat." when I try to access http://mysitename.com/chat/', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'i-get-a-warning-sorry-your-mobile-browser-does-not-support-chat-when-i-try-to-access-httpmysitename-comchat', '', '', '2012-08-23 14:23:44', '2012-08-23 08:53:44', '', 0, 'http://www.cometchat.com/answers/?p=1235', 0, 'post', '', 0),
