(1240, 1, '2012-05-18 15:28:18', '2012-05-18 09:58:18', '# Configuring the module\n\nYou can hide games with the help of *banned keywords* by adding them in the area provided and then clicking on the *Update Settings* button.	\n\nAll the games which have these banned keywords will be hidden.\n\n![Games Settings]\n(http://v6.cometchat.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/games+settings.png)', 'Games', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'games', '', '', '2012-05-18 15:28:18', '2012-05-18 09:58:18', '', 4625, 'http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/?page_id=1240', 16, 'page', '', 0),
(1246, 1, '2012-08-23 14:30:07', '2012-08-23 09:00:07', 'If you want to change the CSS inside each plugin or module, you can find the css file as:\n\n<strong>/cometchat/&lt;modules or plugins&gt;/&lt;module or plugin name&gt;/themes/&lt;theme name&gt;/&lt;module or plugin name&gt;.css</strong>', 'How do I change the CSS for a particular plugin/module?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'how-do-i-change-the-css-for-a-particular-pluginmodule', '', '', '2012-08-23 14:30:07', '2012-08-23 09:00:07', '', 0, 'http://www.cometchat.com/answers/?p=1246', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(1248, 1, '2012-08-23 14:33:13', '2012-08-23 09:03:13', 'For Real Time translate configuration, you need to sign up for the Microsoft Translator service.\n\nThere are various Subscriptions available and you can select a Subscription depending on your requirements.\n\nFor more details on how to proceed, please refer to the following URL:\n\n<strong><em>http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/admin/modules/real-time-translate</em></strong>', 'I want to use Microsoft Translate API module but it always says ''Please configure this module using CometChat Administration Panel''. ', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'i-want-to-use-microsoft-translate-api-module-but-it-always-says-please-configure-this-module-using-cometchat-administration-panel', '', '', '2012-08-23 14:33:13', '2012-08-23 09:03:13', '', 0, 'http://www.cometchat.com/answers/?p=1248', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(1258, 1, '2012-08-23 14:21:47', '2012-08-23 08:51:47', 'You can hide CometChat bar on your website by using the following steps:\n\nGo to <strong>CometChat Administration Panel</strong> -&gt; <strong>settings</strong> -&gt; set <strong>"Hide Bar for non-logged in users"</strong> to <strong>"Yes"</strong> and click on the <strong>Update Settings</strong> button as shown in the figure below.\n\n<img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/hide1.png" alt="hide1" />\n', 'I want to hide CometChat bar for non-logged users on my website', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'i-want-to-hide-cometchat-bar-for-non-logged-users-on-my-website', '', '', '2012-08-23 14:21:47', '2012-08-23 08:51:47', '', 0, 'http://www.cometchat.com/answers/?p=1258', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(1267, 1, '2012-05-31 12:44:52', '2012-05-31 07:14:52', '', 'Hide', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', 'hide', '', '', '2012-05-31 12:44:52', '2012-05-31 07:14:52', '', 0, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Hide.png', 0, 'attachment', 'image/png', 0),
(1270, 1, '2012-08-23 14:22:13', '2012-08-23 08:52:13', 'Yes, you can do it. To do so, follow the steps given below:\n\nGo to <strong>CometChat Administration Panel</strong> -&gt; <strong>Settings</strong> -&gt; <strong>Banned words &amp; users</strong> and delete everything from <strong>"Banned Words"</strong> and click on <strong>"Modify"</strong> as shown in  the image below.\n\n<img src="http://v6.cometchat.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/banned.png" alt="banned" />\n\n', 'I want to disable the filtering of banned words while chatting. Can I do it?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'i-want-to-disable-the-filtering-of-banned-words-while-chatting-can-i-do-it', '', '', '2012-08-23 14:22:13', '2012-08-23 08:52:13', '', 0, 'http://www.cometchat.com/answers/?p=1270', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(1273, 1, '2012-06-01 16:09:20', '2012-06-01 10:39:20', 'You can view a demo by pointing your mobile browser to:\n\n<strong>http://www.cometchat.com/chat/</strong>', 'I want to view a demo of the mobile chat app from my iPhone. How can I do it?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'i-want-to-view-a-demo-of-the-mobile-chat-app-from-my-iphone-how-can-i-do-it', '', '', '2012-06-01 16:09:20', '2012-06-01 10:39:20', '', 0, 'http://www.cometchat.com/answers/?p=1273', 0, 'post', '', 0),
