(1360, 1, '2012-05-18 15:07:54', '2012-05-18 09:37:54', 'You have the option to set CometChat to show all the online users or all the friends in the *"Who''s Online" List.*\n\n![Who''s Online List]\n(http://v6.cometchat.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/whos-online-list.png)\n\n&gt; Displaying all online users is recommended for small sites only\n\n&gt; If your CometChat Admin Panel does not have this section, then your site does not have a friends feature so CometChat will automatically show all online users.', 'Who''s Online List', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'whos-online-list', '', '', '2012-05-18 15:07:54', '2012-05-18 09:37:54', '', 78, 'http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/?page_id=1360', 18, 'page', '', 0),
(1362, 1, '2012-04-30 16:14:10', '2012-04-30 10:44:10', '', 'Who''s Online List', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', 'whos-online-list', '', '', '2012-04-30 16:14:10', '2012-04-30 10:44:10', '', 0, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/whos-online-list.png', 5, 'attachment', 'image/png', 0),
(1383, 1, '2012-05-18 15:09:17', '2012-05-18 09:39:17', 'CometService offloads 95% of work to our servers and reduces message delivery time.	\n\nCometService can be activated directly from the CometChat Administration Panel. \n\nTo use CometService, you need to perform two easy steps.\n\n# Obtaining Keys\n\n1. Point your browser to [http://www.cometchat.com/cometservice](http://www.cometchat.com/cometservice) and select a plan of your choice\n2. After subscribing, you will receive an automated email from us\n3. Login to CometChat.com and visit [http://www.cometchat.com/my/cometservice](http://www.cometchat.com/my/cometservice)\n4. Copy the keys from the page \n\n# Adding the Keys\n1. Login to *CometChat Administration Panel*\n2. Select *Settings -&gt; CometService*\n3. Enter the keys and set *Use CometService* to *Yes*\n\n![Comet Service]\n(http://v6.cometchat.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/CometService.png)\n\n\n', 'CometService', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'comet-service', '', '', '2012-05-18 15:09:17', '2012-05-18 09:39:17', '', 78, 'http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/?page_id=1383', 19, 'page', '', 0),
(1395, 1, '2012-04-30 17:05:23', '2012-04-30 11:35:23', '', 'Comet Service', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', 'cometservice-2', '', '', '2012-04-30 17:05:23', '2012-04-30 11:35:23', '', 0, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/CometService.png', 5, 'attachment', 'image/png', 0),
(1406, 1, '2012-08-23 14:30:43', '2012-08-23 09:00:43', 'CometChat has a feature that displays a <strong>pencil-image</strong> next to the user''s name at the top of the chat window when the user is typing.\n\nHowever, note that this is an experimental feature and may NOT work at all. We provide no support for this feature.\n\nTo enable this feature, set <strong>''DISABLE_ISTYPING''</strong> to <strong>0</strong> in the <strong>/cometchat/config.php</strong> file i.e. \n<strong>define(''DISABLE_ISTYPING'',''0'')</strong>;	', 'How will I know that the other user is typing during an one-on-one conversation?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'how-will-i-know-that-the-other-user-is-typing-during-one-on-one-conversation', '', '', '2012-08-23 14:30:43', '2012-08-23 09:00:43', '', 0, 'http://www.cometchat.com/answers/?p=1406', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(1409, 1, '2012-05-18 15:10:14', '2012-05-18 09:40:14', 'With this feature, you can enable your visitors to automatically log into CometChat when they visit your site as Guests12432 etc.\n\nYou can configure which set of users will be displayed in the Who’s Online List for logged in users as well as for visitors.		\n\n#Guest Chat Configuration		\n1. Login to *CometChat Administration Panel*	\n\n2. Select *Settings -&gt; Guest Chat*	\n\n3. Enable *Guest Chat*	\n\n4. Set the *Prefix for guest names, Who’s Online List for guests* and *logged in users* accordingly.	\n\n5. Click on the *Update* button		\n\n![Guest Chat](http://v6.cometchat.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/guestchat.png)', 'Guest Chat', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'guest-chat', '', '', '2012-05-18 15:10:14', '2012-05-18 09:40:14', '', 78, 'http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/?page_id=1409', 20, 'page', '', 0),
(1414, 1, '2012-08-23 14:26:21', '2012-08-23 08:56:21', 'CometChat loses its layout on your website because of incorrect loading of the CSS file. \n\nIf the CSS is not loading, follow the set of procedures listed below:\n\n	<li>\n\n<ol>\n\nLoad <strong>cometchat/css.php</strong> in the browser and save the contents into <strong>cometchat/cometchat.css file</strong>.\n\n</ol>\n\n </li>\n	<li>\n<ol>\n\nEdit the CometChat HTML code to point to the <strong>cometchat/cometchat.css</strong> file instead of the <strong>cometchat/css.php</strong>\n\n</ol>\n\n\n</li>\n\n	<li>\n\n<ol>\n\n\nMake sure that the CometChat HTML code is added immediately after the <strong> head tag </strong>of your site.\n\n</ol>\n\n</li>\n\n', 'CometChat looses its layout on my website and sometimes works fine after I reload the page. What could be the issue?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'cometchat-looses-its-layout-on-my-website-and-sometimes-works-fine-after-i-reload-the-page-what-could-be-the-issue', '', '', '2012-08-23 14:26:21', '2012-08-23 08:56:21', '', 0, 'http://www.cometchat.com/answers/?p=1414', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(1417, 1, '2012-04-30 17:28:16', '2012-04-30 11:58:16', '', 'Guest Chat', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', 'guest-chat', '', '', '2012-04-30 17:28:16', '2012-04-30 11:58:16', '', 0, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Guest-Chat.png', 5, 'attachment', 'image/png', 0),
(1434, 1, '2012-05-18 15:11:12', '2012-05-18 09:41:12', 'With this feature you can ban a particular user or add words to the list of abusive words.			\n\n![banned words](http://v6.cometchat.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/bannedwords.png)	\n\nTo know the ID of a user, click on the Don’t know ID link and enter the username in the new window that opens and then click on the *Search Database* button.		\n\n![Find User ID](http://v6.cometchat.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Find+User+ID+1.png)	\n\nBanned users will not be able to use IM and chatroom functionality of CometChat	\n\n<blockquote>\n<p>Please use comma to separate IDs and words</p>\n</blockquote>', 'Banned words and users', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'banned-words-and-users', '', '', '2012-05-18 15:11:12', '2012-05-18 09:41:12', '', 78, 'http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/?page_id=1434', 21, 'page', '', 0),
