(1507, 1, '2012-06-11 14:27:52', '2012-06-11 08:57:52', '', 'embedCR', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', 'embedcr', '', '', '2012-06-11 14:27:52', '2012-06-11 08:57:52', '', 0, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/embedCR.png', 0, 'attachment', 'image/png', 0),
(1519, 1, '2012-08-23 14:27:56', '2012-08-23 08:57:56', 'If you are facing this issue, then you need to change the permission of <strong>/cometchat/config.php</strong> file.\n\nChange the file permission to <strong>777 (read/write/execute)</strong> so that all the changes made through the CometChat Administration Panel are reflected on your site.', 'The changes I make in the CometChat Administration Panel are not reflected on my site. What is the issue?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'the-changes-that-i-make-in-the-cometchat-administration-panel-are-not-reflected-on-my-site-what-is-the-issue', '', '', '2012-08-23 14:27:56', '2012-08-23 08:57:56', '', 0, 'http://www.cometchat.com/answers/?p=1519', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(1521, 1, '2012-05-18 15:12:32', '2012-05-18 09:42:32', 'If the Base URL is incorrect, CometChat will stop working on your site.\n\n#Update Base URL\nIf you are using CometChat over a cross domain or sub domain then the *Base URL detection algorithm* may fail to detect your site''s *base URL*. Therefore in this case you will have to put the **Base URL manually**.\n\nFor example, if *www.yoursite.com* is your **main domain** and **CometChat** is **installed at alternate domain** i.e. *www.chat.yoursite1.com*, in this case your base URL will be *http://www.chat.yoursite1.com* \n\n![Update Base URL new]\n(http://v6.cometchat.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Update+base+URL+new.png)\n\nIn most cases, your *Base URL* will be */cometchat/*', 'Change Base URL', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'change-base-url', '', '', '2012-05-18 15:12:32', '2012-05-18 09:42:32', '', 78, 'http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/?page_id=1521', 22, 'page', '', 0),
(1529, 1, '2012-08-23 14:32:37', '2012-08-23 09:02:37', 'To reduce load on your Server:\n\n1. Make sure all your tables are <strong>InnoDB</strong> (it supports row level locking instead of table locking).\n \n2. Run <strong>www.yoursite.com/cometchat/cron.php</strong> every 3 hours to clear your CometChat table entries.\n \n3. You can avoid <strong>execution of MySQL queries</strong> against your database and improve the performance of the chat system by subscribing to our <strong><a href="http://www.cometchat.com/cometservice">CometService</a></strong> which offloads 95% of the work to our servers.\n\nWe also provide <a href="http://www.cometchat.com/cometservice/third-party-alternatives">alternative transports</a>- self-hosted APE server, PubNub, PusherApp and BeaconPush which can be used instead of CometService.', 'After installing CometChat, the load on our server is high. What can I do to reduce this load?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'after-installing-cometchat-the-load-on-our-server-is-high-what-can-i-do-to-reduce-this-load', '', '', '2012-08-23 14:32:37', '2012-08-23 09:02:37', '', 0, 'http://www.cometchat.com/answers/?p=1529', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(1540, 1, '2012-04-30 22:45:53', '2012-04-30 17:15:53', '', 'Update Base URL1', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', 'updatebaseurl1', '', '', '2012-04-30 22:45:53', '2012-04-30 17:15:53', '', 0, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Update+Base+URL1.png', 5, 'attachment', 'image/png', 0),
(1543, 1, '2012-05-18 15:13:37', '2012-05-18 09:43:37', 'This feature allows you to *disable* CometChat temporarily on your site.\n\nTo disable CometChat, set the option to *Yes* and then click on the *Update* button.\n\n![Disable CometChat]\n(http://v6.cometchat.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Disable+CometChat.png)', 'Disable CometChat', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'disable-cometchat', '', '', '2012-05-18 15:13:37', '2012-05-18 09:43:37', '', 78, 'http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/?page_id=1543', 25, 'page', '', 0),
(1548, 1, '2012-04-30 23:03:44', '2012-04-30 17:33:44', '', 'Disable CometChat', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', 'disablecometchat', '', '', '2012-04-30 23:03:44', '2012-04-30 17:33:44', '', 0, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Disable+CometChat.png', 5, 'attachment', 'image/png', 0),
(1558, 1, '2012-05-18 15:13:15', '2012-05-18 09:43:15', 'To change your username and password go to  *CometChat Administration Panel -&gt; Settings  -&gt; Change Admin User / Pass.*\n		\nEnter your new username and password, then click on the *Change User/Pass* button.\n\n![Change administration username and password](http://v6.cometchat.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Change+administration+username+and+password.png)\n\n*Note:* Do not use ''or  in your username or password.\n', 'Change Admin User/Pass', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'change-admin-userpass', '', '', '2012-05-18 15:13:15', '2012-05-18 09:43:15', '', 78, 'http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/?page_id=1558', 23, 'page', '', 0),
(1560, 1, '2012-04-30 23:24:45', '2012-04-30 17:54:45', '', 'Change administration username and password', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', 'changeadministrationusernameandpassword', '', '', '2012-04-30 23:24:45', '2012-04-30 17:54:45', '', 0, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Change+administration+username+and+password.png', 5, 'attachment', 'image/png', 0),
(1569, 1, '2012-05-18 15:03:47', '2012-05-18 09:33:47', 'You can add *custom advertisements* to chat boxes and earn money when your users chat. Advertisements will be automatically displayed in the active chat box.\nYou can use any *custom HTML code* as per your requirements.	\n\n#Configuring the Module\n\n1. In the *Extensions* section, add the *Advertisement extension* to your live extensions and click on the *Configure Module* icon besides the name.	\n\n2. Enter your *Advertisement HTML code* and set the *Ad height*.	\n\n3. Click on the *Update Settings* button and close the window.		\n\n![Advertisement Settings](http://v6.cometchat.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Advertisement+Settings.png)', 'Advertisements', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'advertisements', '', '', '2012-05-18 15:03:47', '2012-05-18 09:33:47', '', 630, 'http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/?page_id=1569', 15, 'page', '', 0),
(1580, 1, '2012-05-01 12:12:44', '2012-05-01 06:42:44', '', 'Live Extensions', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', 'liveextensions', '', '', '2012-05-01 12:12:44', '2012-05-01 06:42:44', '', 0, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Live+Extensions.png', 5, 'attachment', 'image/png', 0),
