(1611, 1, '2012-05-01 12:49:32', '2012-05-01 07:19:32', '', 'Facebook+Gtalk+settings', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', 'facebookgtalksettings', '', '', '2012-05-01 12:49:32', '2012-05-01 07:19:32', '', 0, 'http://v6.cometchat.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Facebook+Gtalk+settings.png', 5, 'attachment', 'image/png', 0),
(1616, 1, '2012-08-23 14:35:21', '2012-08-23 09:05:21', 'To display time in your chat conversation, find the code given below in <strong>themes/[THEME-NAME]/css/cometchat.css</strong>\n\n<code><pre>.cometchat_ts {\n        color: #ccc;\n        cursor: default;\n        <strong>display: none;</strong>\n        font-size: 10px;\n        padding-left: 5px;\n        padding-top: 2px;\n        text-align: left;\n}</pre><code>\n\nReplace it with the following code:\n\n<code><pre>.cometchat_ts {\n        color: #ccc;\n        cursor: default;\n        <strong>display: inline;</strong>\n        font-size: 10px;\n        padding-left: 5px;\n        padding-top: 2px;\n        text-align: left;\n}</pre><code>\n\n<blockquote>Note: CometChat 4.4+ has a caching mechanism and so you need to clear the content of <strong>/cometchat/cache directory</strong> when you manually make any changes to CometChat files.</blockquote>\n', 'I want to permanently display chat time in the chat conversation. How can I do that?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'i-want-to-permanently-display-chat-time-in-the-chat-conversation-how-can-i-do-that', '', '', '2012-08-23 14:35:21', '2012-08-23 09:05:21', '', 0, 'http://www.cometchat.com/answers/?p=1616', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(1628, 1, '2012-08-23 14:34:23', '2012-08-23 09:04:23', 'If you are not using CometService, you cannot completely disable logs. This is because your mySQL table is used to transport data from the sender to the receiver. \n\nHowever, you can clean up the tables periodically by running the following cronjob every 3 hours:\n\n<strong>http://www.yoursite.com/cometchat/cron.php</strong>\n\nIf you are using CometService,\n\nYou can set <strong>"Save Logs"</strong> to <strong>"No"</strong> through <strong>CometChat Administration Panel</strong>.\n\nClick on <strong>Settings</strong> tab -&gt; <strong>Comet Service</strong> -&gt; Select <strong>"No"</strong> option for <strong>Save logs?</strong> -&gt; Click on <strong>"Update Settings"</strong> button.\n', 'I don''t want CometChat to store saved logs. How do I disable the save logs option?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'i-dont-want-cometchat-to-store-saved-logs-how-do-i-disable-the-save-logs-option', '', '', '2012-08-23 14:34:23', '2012-08-23 09:04:23', '', 0, 'http://www.cometchat.com/answers/?p=1628', 0, 'post', '', 0),
