(1899, 1, '2012-05-18 15:00:05', '2012-05-18 09:30:05', 'CometChat offers *8 additional languages* with which you can manage the language of the CometChat bar and plugins. You also have the option to add new languages to the existing list.\n\nLanguages that CometChat offers includes\n\n1. Chinese\n2. Portuguese\n3. Japanese\n4. Italian\n5. French\n6. Spanish\n7. German\n8. Arabic\n\n#Preview a language\n\nWith this option, you can have a view of all the sections of CometChat in the language of your choice.\n\nFor example, click on the *Preview Language* button next to French to get a view of all the sections of CometChat that has been translated to *French*.\n \n![Language preview]\n(http://v6.cometchat.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Language+preview.png)\n\n#Add Language\n\nTo import a language to the existing list of languages, click on the *Add Language* button.', 'Additional languages', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'additional-languages', '', '', '2012-05-18 15:00:05', '2012-05-18 09:30:05', '', 72, 'http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/?page_id=1899', 17, 'page', '', 0),
