(2500, 1, '2012-06-13 16:42:58', '2012-06-13 11:12:58', '# Basic Edition\n\nBasic Edition is for small sites.	\n\nThis is a *branded edition* which offers *10 modules* and *10 plugins* for unlimited users.	\n\nYou can provide the following guide to your site users:	\n\n[User Manual for Basic Edition](http://v6.cometchat.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/End-user-manual-Basic-Edition.pdf)	\n	\n(Right click to save the file to your computer)	\n\n#Professional Edition	\n\nThis is *branding free* edition. Apart from the features of Basic Edition, this edition offers the following features:		\n\n* *Facebook/Gtalk Friends Chat*\n* *Transliterate Plugin*\n* *Save Conversation Plugin*\n* *Real-time Conversations Translation Module*\n\nYou can provide the following guide to your site users:	\n\n[User Manual for Professional Edition](http://v6.cometchat.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/End-user-manual-Professional-Edition.pdf)	\n\n(Right click to save the file to your computer)	\n\n#Premium Edition	\n\nPremium Edition is preferable for commercial sites.\n\nThis edition has all the features of Professional Edition and also includes the following additional features:\n\n* *Mobile web-apps*\n* *Advertisements Extension*\n* *Whiteboard Plugin*\n* *Guaranteed Installation*	\n\nYou can provide the following guide to your site users:	\n\n[User Manual for Premium Edition](http://v6.cometchat.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/End-user-manual-Premium-Edition.pdf)	\n\n#Platinum Edition\n\nThis edition has all the features of the Premium Edition plus\n\n* *Audio &amp; Video Chat Plugin*\n* *Screen sharing Plugin*\n* *XMPP/Jabber Support*	\n* *Broadcast Plugin*	\n\nYou can provide the following guide to your site users:	\n\n[User Manual for Platinum Edition](http://v6.cometchat.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/End-user-manual-Platinum-Edition.pdf)		\n\n(Right click to save the file to your computer)\n\n	', 'End User Manual', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'end-user-manual', '', '', '2012-06-13 16:42:58', '2012-06-13 11:12:58', '', 0, 'http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/?page_id=2500', 110, 'page', '', 0),
