(2954, 1, '2012-06-18 16:12:05', '2012-06-18 10:42:05', 'If you would like to self-host Adobe FMS server,\n\n* Purchase, download and install Adobe FMS on your server (outside support scope)\n\nIf you would like to use a third-party Adobe FMS host,\n\n* Sign up with a host like [http://www.influxis.com/](http://www.influxis.com/)\n\n#Installing Audio/Video Chat Plugin with FMS\n\nCreate a folder named ***''avchat''*** in the applications directory of your FMS.	\n		\nFor example, if you are using FMS v4.5 on windows system then you need to create the ***avchat*** folder in **''*C:Program FilesAdobeFlash Media Server 4.5applications*''** folder.\n\n#Configuring the Audio/Video Chat Plugin\n\n* In the ***CometChat Admin Panel*** -&gt; ***Plugins*** section, add the ***Audio/Video Chat Plugin*** to your live plugins and click on the ***config*** link besides the name.\n	\n* Enter the required details.	\n		\n* Click on the ***Update Settings*** button and close the window.\n\n![Configuring the plugin]\n(http://v6.cometchat.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/FMS1-e1339765891339.png)', 'FMS (RTMFP)', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'fms-rtmfp', '', '', '2012-06-18 16:12:05', '2012-06-18 10:42:05', '', 2881, 'http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/?page_id=2954', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(2961, 1, '2012-06-18 16:12:10', '2012-06-18 10:42:10', 'Uses only peer-to-peer technology and does not require any servers. Not recommended as firewalls may block UDP ports required for data transfer.\n\nTo use this server select ****Stratus**** from the ***Technology Dropdown*** box. Enter all the values for Stratus settings and click on the ***Update Settings*** button.\n\n![Configuring the plugin]\n(http://v6.cometchat.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/stratus-e1339765989121.png)', 'Stratus', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'stratus', '', '', '2012-06-18 16:12:10', '2012-06-18 10:42:10', '', 2881, 'http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/?page_id=2961', 0, 'page', '', 0),
