(3976, 1, '2012-12-20 18:18:43', '2012-12-20 12:48:43', '1) You need to download the latest version of [Footer Manager Extension](http://coding.bezslabostei.ru/FooterManager/Download) and extract it into the\nextensions folder of your MediaWiki installation.\n\n2) Enable the extension by adding this line to your LocalSettings.php file:\n\n`require_once (''extensions/FooterManager/FooterManager.php'');`\n\n3) For CometChat to appear on your site, you need to make following changes in the *extensions/FooterManager/FooterManager.php* file.\ni) Assign the footer code to the key ‘headscript’.\nii) Assign the value of key ‘icon’ and ‘bottomscript’ to null.\n\nFor example:\n\n`$wgFooterManagerBanners[] = array(\n''headscript'' =&gt; '''',\n''icon'' =&gt; '''',\n''bottomscript'' =&gt;'''',\n);`', 'MediaWiki', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'mediawiki', '', '', '2012-12-20 18:18:43', '2012-12-20 12:48:43', '', 146, 'http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/?page_id=3976', 100, 'page', '', 0),
