(4034, 1, '2013-02-28 14:00:02', '2013-02-28 08:30:02', 'CometChat can integrate with virtually any custom coded site. Sometimes it may not be possible to install PHP/mySQL on your existing server. Using these guides you can install CometChat on a separate sub-domain and add only only a few lines of HTML code to your site template.\n\nFor more details, please select a guide:', 'Advanced', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'advanced', '', '', '2013-02-28 14:00:02', '2013-02-28 08:30:02', '', 4439, 'http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/?page_id=4034', 68, 'page', '', 0),
