(4164, 1, '2013-03-14 16:40:22', '2013-03-14 11:10:22', 'With this feature your site users will get the latest notifications of all the newly arrived messages, on clicking these alerts he or she will get access to CometChat mobile web app where they can view all the messages.\n\n#Configuring the extension	\n\n1. In the Extensions section, add the *Mobile Tab extension* to your *live extensions* and click on the *config* link besides the name.	\n\n2. Enter the size of mobiletab in percentile (100% corresponds to default size of the mobiletab)	\n\n3. Click on the *Update Settings* button and close the window.	\n\n![Mobile Tab](http://v6.cometchat.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/mobiletab.png)', 'Mobile Tab', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'mobile-tab', '', '', '2013-03-14 16:40:22', '2013-03-14 11:10:22', '', 630, 'http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/?page_id=4164', 16, 'page', '', 0),
