(4225, 1, '2013-03-14 16:24:32', '2013-03-14 10:54:32', '* Point your browser to the following URL: *https://developer.addlive.com/cometchat* or click on the link in the plugin setting window to create an AddLive account if you don’t have an Application ID and an Application Auth Secret key	\n\n* Register on the site with the required details		\n\n* Once you are done with the registration process, you will receive a mail from AddLive containing the Application ID and Stable API key	\n\n* Now place these values in plugin setting window and click on the *Update* settings	\n\n![AddLive](http://v6.cometchat.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/addlive_full.png)', 'AddLive', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'addlive', '', '', '2013-03-14 16:24:32', '2013-03-14 10:54:32', '', 2881, 'http://www.cometchat.com/documentation/?page_id=4225', 0, 'page', '', 0),
